Sederhana, aku pergi kerja,

250
00:20:33,193 --> 00:20:34,527
telepon Pak Kim, dan berkata,

251
00:20:34,611 --> 00:20:36,529
"Aku penulis top, Cha Eun-ho.

252
00:20:36,613 --> 00:20:38,531
Aku ingin membatalkan
semua kontrak bukuku.

253
00:20:38,865 --> 00:20:40,950
Seri <i>Kontrak Berdarah</i>, seri <i>Semesta</i>,

254
00:20:41,034 --> 00:20:42,535
