bertanggung jawab padamu.

317
00:24:46,028 --> 00:24:47,780
Apa maksudmu?

318
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:50,616
Astaga, Bu Go.

319
00:24:51,617 --> 00:24:54,287
Kau sangat cantik
saat pertama bekerja di sini.

320
00:24:54,370 --> 00:24:56,497
Tapi kau habiskan masa mudamu
membuat buku.

321
00:24:58,624 --> 00:25:00,126
Berarti aku tak cantik lagi?

322
00:25:03,838 --> 00:25:06,090
Tidak, bukan itu...

323
00:25:07,175 --> 00:25:08,551
Astaga, sudah.

324
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:11,345
Tunggu. Gunting.

325
00:25:12,180 --> 00:25:14,223
Ada di sana. Di sana.

326
00:25:15,766 --> 00:25:17,268
BIsa pegangkan ini?

327
00:25:18,186 --> 00:25:19,812
Kenapa tak terpikir pakai gunting?

328
00:25:29,030 --> 00:25:30,072
Sudah.

329
00:25:35,286 --> 00:25:36,245
Terima kasih.

330
00:25:36,329 --> 00:25:37,538
Bilang jika lepas lagi.

331
00:25:37,622 --> 00:25:38,956
Akan kujahitkan lagi.

332
00:25:39,207 --> 00:25:40,166
Terima kasih.

333
