Astaga, panas.

334
00:26:09,529 --> 00:26:10,655
Kenapa kau tak membaca?

335
00:26:12,031 --> 00:26:12,990
Tidak menarik?

336
00:26:15,117 --> 00:26:17,870
Aku melihat hal
yang lebih bagus dan cantik

337
00:26:18,621 --> 00:26:19,956
dari komik.

338
00:26:20,831 --> 00:26:21,791
Apa itu?

339
00:26:22,833 --> 00:26:24,710
Pacarku.

340
00:26:35,555 --> 00:26:37,014
Astaga, sakit.

341
00:26:57,785 --> 00:26:58,744
Jangan begitu.

342
00:26:59,161 --> 00:27:00,329
Jangan apa?

343
00:27:00,413 --> 00:27:02,498
- Jangan begitu.
- Aku tak lakukan apa pun.

344
00:27:29,233 --> 00:27:30,109
Kau cerdas.

345
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:32,320
Bagaimana

346
00:27:33,696 --> 00:27:34,989
kalau sambil minum bir?

347
00:27:43,998 --> 00:27:44,957
Bagaimana rasanya?

348
00:27:45,499 --> 00:27:46,500
Lezat.

349
00:28:01,641 --> 00:28:02,642
Sudah selesai membaca?

