00:57:17,870 --> 00:57:20,081
Pak Kang Byeong-jun

783
00:57:20,498 --> 00:57:21,499
muncul kembali.

784
00:57:28,548 --> 00:57:29,465
Ini...

785
00:57:29,966 --> 00:57:32,760
Ini naskah Pak Kang.

786
00:57:33,344 --> 00:57:35,471
Novel terakhir yang katanya
akan dia tulis.

787
00:57:36,180 --> 00:57:37,139
<i>Para Pahlawan.</i>

788
00:57:40,017 --> 00:57:41,227
<i>Para Pahlawan.</i>

789
00:57:43,396 --> 00:57:44,689
"Park Jeong-hun"?

