00:58:07,211 --> 00:58:08,754
<i>Pak Kang sakit.</i>

791
00:58:09,922 --> 00:58:13,259
<i>Dan selama ini Eun-ho merawatnya.</i>

792
00:58:22,685 --> 00:58:23,603
Dan-i.

793
00:58:25,730 --> 00:58:26,897
Dan-i, kau di mana?

794
00:58:41,329 --> 00:58:42,496
Dan-i.

795
00:58:44,832 --> 00:58:45,916
Ke mana dia?

796
00:58:55,426 --> 00:58:56,927
Dan-i, kau di loteng?

797
00:58:59,096 --> 00:59:00,431
Aku beli bahan makanan.

798
00:59:03,726 --> 00:59:04,685
Dan-i.

799
00:59:16,697 --> 00:59:17,990
Pak Kang...

800
00:59:22,078 --> 00:59:23,621
Kau merawatnya, 'kan?

801
00:59:27,083 --> 00:59:27,917
Di Kapyong...

802
00:59:29,794 --> 00:59:31,504
Pak Kang di Kapyong, 'kan?

803
00:59:41,305 --> 00:59:42,223
<i>Aku selalu takut</i>

804
00:59:43,683 --> 00:59:46,727
<i>kotak itu akan terbuka dan dunia tahu</i>

805
00:59:47,228 --> 00:59:49,021
<i>soal kisah ini.</i>

806
00:59:50,314 --> 00:59:53,067
<i>Saat berpikir mungkin aku telah salah</i>

807
00:59:54,110 --> 00:59:55,236
<i>membuat keputusan,</i>

808
00:59:56,487 --> 00:59:59,907
<i>aku takut pada kecaman
dan tak bisa tidur pada malam hari.</i>

809
01:00:01,867 --> 01:00:03,077
<i>Kupikir mungkin selama ini</i>

810
01:00:04,286 --> 01:00:06,455
<i>aku ingin Dan-i tahu segalanya.</i>

811
01:00:08,207 --> 01:00:10,084
<i>Meskipun dunia membenciku,</i>

812
